  "cooking_instructions": [
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Boil a kettle</p><p>Add your <strong>gluten free linguine</strong> to a pot of<strong> boiled water </strong>with a large pinch of <strong>salt</strong> and bring to the boil over a high heat</p><p>Cook the linguine<strong> </strong>for 8-10 min or until it's cooked with a slight bite</p><p>Once done, drain and reserve a cup of the <strong>starchy pasta water</strong></p>",
